Package Util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSVOutput
    The CSVOutput class creates the CSV output for each Defects4j bug that is processed by the GP.
    Firebase
    The Firebase class provides helper functions for post methods to be constructed and sent to a valid Firebase endpoint.
    Javadoc
    The Javadoc class produces HTML documents for this project and outputs to the /javadoc directory.
    MutationHelpers
    The MutationHelpers class provides helper functions for collecting nodes and types of the given AST program.
    ParserRunner
    The ParserRunner class splits the YAML configuration file into three objects; Defects4J, GP and Output, and defers the validation and parsing of these to their respective YAMLParser classes.
    ProjectPaths
    The ProjectPaths class provides helper functions for accessing the file system of the project and fetching buggy and fixed Defects4J patches.
    ShellProcessBuilder
    The ShellProcessBuilder class creates process builders that can interact with the systems command line to interact with the Defects4j cli.
    ValidDefectsPatches
    The ValidDefectsPatches class uploads the valid Defects4j bugs to the Vue website.
